{"tid":2202242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴城巴page出post 串鳩話usb充電頭會電親佢仔女嘅家長","createTime":"2020-09-14T12:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T12:27:08.000Z","uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fe5c075a058eecebbbc377c563b51dbde9172a","tid":2202242,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/222711055143535/posts/789339028480732/?extid=IkJqpTRceSLcN0mx&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F222711055143535%2Fposts%2F789339028480732%2F%3Fextid%3DIkJqpTRceSLcN0mx%26d%3Dn&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=f548ed1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/222711055143535/posts/789339028480732/?extid=IkJqpTRceSLcN0mx&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehPrHjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehPrHjD.jpg&h=7af26de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【充電插頭好安全🔋】<br />\n<br />\n近日小編喺網上見到有家長好擔心巴士上嘅充電插頭會電親小朋友。小編即刻請教一下工程部嘅同事，問下有無危險⚠️。<br />\n<br />\n工程部嘅同事表示：「放心啦！我哋巴士嘅充電插頭只有 5V直流電輸出，單頭嘅插頭電流輸出係2.1A；而雙頭插頭嘅電流就係3A，每個插頭最多只有1.5A（實際情況視乎電子產品及充電線規格）。成個USB充電系統都只係一個特低電壓嘅電力系統，非常安全。而且所有USB插頭都符合國際安全標準，唔會咁易漏電。所以即管放心使用啦！」<br />\n<br />\n現時我哋新款巴士嘅座椅椅背，都配備咗獨立USB充電插頭喇！只要有充電線，就可以幫你嘅電子設備充返電，打機🎮覆email✉️都一樣唔怕無電啦！小編試過用嚟幫相機📷充電，一樣無問題～唔知你地有無畀巴士充電插頭救過一命嘅經歷呢？留言話畀我哋知啦！<br />\n<br />\n#新巴 #城巴 #NWFB #Citybus #新巴城巴小知識 #USB充電插頭 #符合安全標準 #電話無電救您一命 #不可插入手指 #愛護公物 #請小心照顧同行兒童<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a9bc8237fa3ec7cc4b2cf9faf471ef73f96295","tid":2202242,"uid":91833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"請問邊句寸"},{"pid":"8275a57ff9a391177aa907d5263d2a09e65c1c57","tid":2202242,"uid":127425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"個家長真係柒到核爆"},{"pid":"0c7faba65059c135a4f957291cbfd414331de39e","tid":2202242,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"我淨係想知仲有冇提供法律援助俾970車長？"},{"pid":"fca6a532740baaee159003ce5abff41ebf121ef6","tid":2202242,"uid":110579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"電鐘都有電<br />\n位家長唔好撳鐘落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80e6647a10982322148a539ae345edb57288c57","tid":2202242,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">不可插入手指 #愛護公物 #請小心照顧同行兒童<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}